sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Cliente/Aplicación
    participant MainProxy as ConsultaPlanesCredito.proxy
    participant RutaRegional as consultaRutaRegional_db
    participant HNProxy as ConsultaPlanesCreditoHN.proxy
    participant ConvertPais as convertirCodigoPais
    participant HNDatabase as MasterDataHN/conDatosPlanes_db
    participant HNOracle as Oracle Database HN
    participant MapeoErrores as MapeoErrores.proxy
    participant ErrorHandler as Manejador de Errores

    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: Flujo Honduras (HN01) - ConsultaPlanesCredito

    Client->>MainProxy: SOAP Request
    Note right of Client: Header: SourceBank=HN01<br/>Body: ACCOUNT_NUMBER, ORG

    MainProxy->>MainProxy: Validar Esquema XML
    Note right of MainProxy: Validar campos obligatorios<br/>ACCOUNT_NUMBER no vacío

    alt Validación Fallida
        MainProxy->>ErrorHandler: Error de Validación
        ErrorHandler->>MainProxy: Respuesta de Error
        MainProxy->>Client: SOAP Fault
    end

    MainProxy->>RutaRegional: Consultar Ruta Regional
    Note right of RutaRegional: ServiceId: FICBCO0321<br/>Region: HN01<br/>Version: V2

    RutaRegional->>RutaRegional: Consultar BD Regional
    
    alt Región No Válida
        RutaRegional->>MainProxy: PV_CODIGO_ERROR != SUCCESS
        MainProxy->>MapeoErrores: Mapear Error Regional
        MapeoErrores->>MainProxy: Error Mapeado
        MainProxy->>Client: Response con Error
    end

    RutaRegional->>MainProxy: PV_UBICACION=ConsultaPlanesCreditoHN
    Note left of RutaRegional: PV_CODIGO_ERROR=SUCCESS<br/>PV_UBICACION=Middleware/v2/ProxyServices/ConsultaPlanesCreditoHN

    MainProxy->>MainProxy: Enrutamiento Dinámico
    Note right of MainProxy: Router Dinámico:<br/>service=ConsultaPlanesCreditoHN

    MainProxy->>HNProxy: Invocar Proxy HN
    Note right of HNProxy: Transport: HTTP<br/>Endpoint: /Middleware/v2/ProxyServices/ConsultaPlanesCreditoHN

    HNProxy->>ConvertPais: Convertir Código País
    Note right of ConvertPais: Conversión: HN01 → HND<br/>Sentido: OSB-ISO3

    ConvertPais->>HNProxy: Código País Convertido
    Note left of ConvertPais: Resultado: HND

    HNProxy->>HNProxy: Transformar Request (XQuery)
    Note right of HNProxy: conDatosPlanesHNIn.xq<br/>Mapear ACCOUNT_NUMBER → PV_CUENTA<br/>Mapear ORG → PV_ORG<br/>Mapear HND → PV_CODIGO_PAIS

    HNProxy->>HNProxy: Validar Request DB
    Note right of HNProxy: Validar esquema XSD<br/>MasterDataHN/conDatosPlanes/xsd/conDatosPlanes_sp

    HNProxy->>HNDatabase: Invocar Stored Procedure
    Note right of HNDatabase: Connection: eis/DB/ConnectionTarjetas<br/>SP: dbo.OSBConDatoPlanes

    HNDatabase->>HNOracle: CALL dbo.OSBConDatoPlanes(PV_CUENTA, PV_ORG, PV_CODIGO_PAIS)
    
    alt Error en Base de Datos
        HNOracle->>HNDatabase: CodigoError != -1
        HNDatabase->>HNProxy: Response con Error
        HNProxy->>HNProxy: Construir Error Response
        Note right of HNProxy: successIndicator: $errorCode<br/>(DIFERENTE a otras regiones)
        HNProxy->>MainProxy: Response con Error
        MainProxy->>MapeoErrores: Mapear Error
        MapeoErrores->>MainProxy: Error Mapeado
        MainProxy->>Client: Response con Error
    end

    HNOracle->>HNDatabase: ResultSet con Planes
    Note left of HNOracle: CodigoError: -1<br/>MensajeError: vacío<br/>RowSet con datos:<br/>- org, cuenta, numseq<br/>- logo, numplan, total_due<br/>- tipo_plan, int_rate<br/>- int_rat1_base, balanceactual<br/>- fecplan, acrd_int<br/>- mora_acrd_int, d2ps_mora_int_per_diem

    HNDatabase->>HNProxy: Response Exitoso

    HNProxy->>HNProxy: Validar Response DB
    Note right of HNProxy: Verificar errorCode != '-1'<br/>Si error: validationMessage = MensajeError<br/>Si éxito: validationMessage = ''

    HNProxy->>HNProxy: Transformar Response (XQuery)
    Note right of HNProxy: consultaPlanesCreditoHNOut.xq<br/>Mapear campos de BD a response:<br/>- org → ORG<br/>- cuenta → ACCOUNT<br/>- numseq → SEQ_NUMBER<br/>- logo → LOGO<br/>- numplan → PLAN_NUMBER<br/>- total_due → PAY_MINIMUM<br/>- tipo_plan → TYPE_PLAN<br/>- int_rate → INT_RATE<br/>- int_rat1_base → INT_RATE_BASE<br/>- balanceactual → CURRENT_BALANCE<br/>- fecplan → DATE_PLAN (yyyyMMdd)<br/>- acrd_int → ACRD_INT<br/>- mora_acrd_int → DELAYS_ACRD_INT<br/>- d2ps_mora_int_per_diem → ACCUMULATED_DELAYS_INT

    HNProxy->>HNProxy: Construir Header de Respuesta
    Note right of HNProxy: Si validationMessage vacío:<br/>successIndicator: Success<br/>Si error:<br/>successIndicator: $errorCode<br/>messages: validationMessage<br/>(ESPECÍFICO DE HN01)

    HNProxy->>MainProxy: SOAP Response
    Note left of HNProxy: Header: successIndicator=Success<br/>Body: CREDIT_PLANS con array de CREDIT_PLAN<br/>Variable: $RSPConDatosPlanes (mayúscula)

    MainProxy->>MainProxy: Validar Response Final
    Note right of MainProxy: Verificar successIndicator != SUCCESS

    alt Response con Error
        MainProxy->>MapeoErrores: Mapear Error Final
        Note right of MapeoErrores: CODIGO_ERROR: successIndicator<br/>MENSAJE_ERROR: FICBCO0321$#$messages
        MapeoErrores->>MainProxy: Error Homologado
        MainProxy->>MainProxy: Actualizar Header Response
    end

    MainProxy->>Client: SOAP Response Final
    Note left of Client: Header: successIndicator, messages<br/>Body: Planes de crédito estructurados<br/>con información completa por plan

    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: Transformaciones Clave HN01:
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 1. Código País: HN01 → HND (OSB-ISO3)
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 2. Fecha: DateTime → yyyyMMdd
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 3. Validación: errorCode != '-1' = éxito
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 4. Conexión BD: eis/DB/ConnectionTarjetas
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 5. SP: dbo.OSBConDatoPlanes (sin SchemaName)
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 6. Transport: HTTP con endpoint específico
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 7. SOAP Selector: SOAP body
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 8. Error Handling: successIndicator=$errorCode (ÚNICO)
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 9. Variable Response: $RSPConDatosPlanes (mayúscula)
    Note over Client, ErrorHandler: 10. Error Handler: messageId + errorCode específico